        <a class="btn btn-light btn-lg" href="#contact" role="button" style="color: black">Let's talk! &raquo;</a></p>
<p><b>Want more information?</b><br>
  <a href="#intro"><i class="fas fa-5x fa-angle-double-down"></i> </a>
</p>
</center>

  </div>
</div>
<section id="intro" class="bg-blue">
